column1: The format of the data is in the following structure:
((x_1,y_1),(x_2,y_2),...,(x_n,y_n)) where x_n is the number of reps for the given set n and y_n is the weight for the given set n.
Each specific combination of reps and weights (i.e. sets) are represented by each tuple respectively.
Note: no consideration has been given to the "creatine lag", usually I take 5ml each day when 1.
